Filters in the assassin folder add filtration to the top lines of the filter you would be normally using.
This code will show weapons used by martial arts skills.

//Assassin Leveling
//Shows magical and rare martial arts weapons, sorted by tier (Normal/Exceptional/Elite) and their appropriate item levels

//Magic Claws
ItemDisplay[ILVL>0 ILVL<35 NORM MAG CL5]: %NAME%
ItemDisplay[ILVL>34 ILVL<66 EXC MAG CL5]: %NAME%
ItemDisplay[ELT MAG CL5]: %NAME%

//Rare Claws
ItemDisplay[ILVL>0 ILVL<35 NORM RARE CL5]: %NAME%
ItemDisplay[ILVL>34 ILVL<66 EXC RARE CL5]: %NAME%
ItemDisplay[ELT RARE CL5]: %NAME%

//Magic Daggers
ItemDisplay[ILVL>0 ILVL<35 NORM MAG WP4]: %NAME%
ItemDisplay[ILVL>34 ILVL<66 EXC MAG WP4]: %NAME%
ItemDisplay[ELT MAG WP4]: %NAME%

//Rare Claws
ItemDisplay[ILVL>0 ILVL<35 NORM RARE WP4]: %NAME%
ItemDisplay[ILVL>34 ILVL<66 EXC RARE WP4]: %NAME%
ItemDisplay[ELT RARE WP4]: %NAME%
